fields.name: Abilities:
fields.value: - Each day, choose a player. The next night, you will play the "Higher or Lower" game with their role.

fields.name: Attributes:
fields.value: - In the "Higher or Lower" game, you first name a number. The host will tell you whether that number is greater than, less than, or equal to your target's role's number. Repeat this process four more times.
